These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-1::.
House: ranch-style, victorian, modern, futuristic
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, singing, card-games, traveling
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, october, august
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, ship, tram, van
 1. the person who's hobby is singing is on the left or right of the person driving the ship##3
 2. the victorian house is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 3. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person driving the tram is on the right of the victorian house##1
 5. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left or far right##3
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in december##3
 7. the modern house is on the left of the victorian house##1
 8. the futuristic house is on the right of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in january##1
11. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the ranch-style house##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2      |      3      |   4   |
| House    | modern   | victorian       | ranch-style | futuristic   |
| Hobby        | singing    | traveling  | card-games      | chess |
| Birthday         | august      | january | october         | december   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | ship       | tram        | van   |

