.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-2::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  bartender, electrician, photographer, police-officer
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, poppy, daisy, tulip
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, card-games, sudoku, magic-tricks
4 different games are played: chess, snooker, poker, billiard
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is card-games##1
2. the electrician is the person who growssunflower##1
3. the person playing poker is the photographer##1
4. the bartender is between the person who growspoppy and the person playing chess##2
5. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
6. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person playing billiard##1
7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the far right##1
8. the person playing chess is on the far left or far right##3
9. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growstulip##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |       3        |      4       |
| Job           | electrician | bartender | police-officer | photographer |
| Flower   | sunflower  | daisy | poppy         | tulip      |
| Hobby         | sudoku      | card-games    | magic-tricks         | skydiving   |
| Game     | chess         | snooker    | billiard          | poker         |

