.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: sunflower, orchid, zinnia, tulip
4 different games are played: billiard, chess, mah-jongg, bridge
4 different pets are kept: cat, dog, hedgehog, turtle
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, thriller, family, musical
 1. the person playing mah-jongg is the person who growszinnia##1
 2. the person playing billiard is on the far left or far right##3
 3. the person who growstulip is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 4. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1
 5. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the person playing bridge##1
 6. the person watching thriller movies is on the left or right of the person watching musical movies##3
 7. the person playing billiard is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 8. the owner of the cat is between the person watching family movies and the person playing chess##2
 9. the person who growstulip is on the left of the person who growssunflower##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the left or right of the person who growstulip##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |     4      |
| Flower          | orchid | tulip  | sunflower | zinnia      |
| Game   | billiard       | bridge    | chess      | mah-jongg      |
| Pet           | turtle     | cat     | dog         | hedgehog   |
| Movie-Genre         | family | disaster | thriller     | musical |

