3. the photographer is the farmhouse house##1
4. the victorian house is on the far left##1
5. the person eating grapefruit is the farmhouse house##1
6. the person eating zucchini is on the far left or far right##3
7. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growspoppy##1
8. the videographer is between the person who growsaconite and the person eating tomato##2
9. the librarian is on the left or right of the person who growspoppy##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |      4       |
| Job           | lawyer     | videographer | librarian | photographer |
| House   | victorian     | tower       | colonial      | farmhouse   |
| Food   | zucchini   | pomegranate   | tomato    | grapefruit       |
| Flower           | aconite | orchid        | balloon-flower    | poppy        |

