.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-5::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, cola, fanta, soy-milk
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, october, august, may
City: hamburg, hannover, paris, colone
There are 4 different nationalities: indian, french, dutch, australian
 1. the indian is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in october##3
 2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in september##3
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the australian##1
 6. the person drinking soy-milk is on the far left or far right##3
 7. the person traveling to hamburg is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in may##3
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the french##1
10. the person traveling to colone is between the person drinking almond-milk and the person traveling to paris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | soy-milk | almond-milk | fanta     | cola       |
| Birthday          | september   | may    | august | october       |
| City   | hamburg     | hannover       | colone    | paris     |
| Nationality         | dutch  | australian  | indian | french |

