 8. the person who growstulip is the art-deco house##1
 9. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the pall-mall-smoker##3
10. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
11. the person who growsiris is the pall-mall-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
