The people use 4 different means of transport: ship, van, bus, snowmobile
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person driving the snowmobile##1
 2. the designer is between the person drinking juice and the person drinking hot-chocolate##2
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the fan of ambient##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 6. the fan of indie is between the person driving the bus and the fan of pop##2
 7. the fan of indie is the person driving the ship##1
 8. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the teacher##1
 9. the writer is on the left or right of the fan of ambient##3
10. the person driving the bus is on the left of the fan of funk##1
11. the fan of ambient is on the left or right of the writer##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |       4       |
| Music-Genre   | pop    | indie  | ambient       | funk  |
