City: nizza, liverpool, prague, san-francisco
 1. the canadian is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 2. the person watching animation movies is the person who growslily##1
 3. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the far left or far right##3
 4. the person who growsdaisy is on the left or right of the person who growsaconite##3
 5. the person who growsaconite is on the left of the egyptian##1
 6. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person traveling to san-francisco##1
 7. the person who growsbegonia is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 8. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person who growsaconite##1
 9. the person traveling to san-francisco is the canadian##1
10. the person traveling to nizza is on the left or right of the thai##3
11. the person watching zombie movies is the person who growsbegonia##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3       |     4     |
| Flower         | begonia      | aconite | daisy       | lily   |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie     | documentary | martial-arts | animation |
| Nationality   | italian    | thai     | egyptian        | canadian       |
| City     | prague | liverpool   | nizza   | san-francisco       |

