.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-3-20::.
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, dog, pony, bird
City: nizza, berlin, paris, new-york
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, mystery, satire
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, chestnut, green, ivory
 1. the owner of the rabbit is on the far right##1
 2. the person who likes chestnut is on the right of the person traveling to nizza##1
 3. the owner of the dog is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
 4. the person traveling to berlin is between the person who likes green and the person who likes chestnut##2
 5. the person watching adventure movies is on the left or right of the owner of the pony##3
 6. the person watching adventure movies is between the person traveling to berlin and the person who likes red##2
 7. the person watching mystery movies is the person traveling to new-york##1
 8. the person watching mystery movies is on the right of the person watching satire movies##1
 9. the owner of the pony is the person traveling to berlin##1
10. the person watching adventure movies is the person traveling to paris##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3     |     4     |
| Pet          | dog | bird   | pony   | rabbit |
| City           | nizza   | paris     | berlin   | new-york |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy    | adventure    | satire   | mystery   |
| Color         | red    | chestnut | ivory | green    |

 